	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sega used to say that Sonic was the fastest video game character. But Mario is quite fast too, especially when you hold down the B button.<br /><br />Then I thought about, what if SMB scrolling was multiplied with 2. Would probably mean that the game would be quite impossible to play. <br /><br />Still it would be fun to play it that way. Has anyone tried to modify it this way? Perhaps a Game Genie code could get this effect?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
